column5: My buddy an I went out this morning, 9 walleye all in the slot..
Nice fish... great way to spend a morning
Very nice fish, congrats and thanks for posting.
why is everybody comgratulating me for not being able to keep any?   LOL I had a blast nonetheless .  Secret Fishin' Holw   SHHHH!
UPDATE:    it's 4: 15  I just got back from round 2 and  managed to keep 2 out of 4.. I might go back out after supper with my wife.
Nice catch !!!! great sized walleyes.  ...cheers  and for round 2,you now have a nice walleye dinner,what time will that be????LOL..LOL..LOL   i can be there in 4 hors....cheers
